# #458 F10-6 expansion: Dir-record emitters for the devproc / devnet /
# devblk backings the audit (docs/audit_arch_shortcuts_2026-06-13.md §8)
# called out as still emitting NAME\n. SYS_LISTDIR_RECORDS now routes
