        # payload (the supervisor's whole registry slot — see the
        # layout in fs/procfs.ad) and is hostowner-only. There is no
        # human-typeable text equivalent — the text-verb /proc/svc/ctl
        # surface covers `unpublish <name>` for delete + the verb set
        # (start/stop/restart/...). The publish push stays a syscall
