            # ("svc_ctl_poll: hostowner-required (uid=NNNN)") matches the
            # other kernel-internal hostowner ops and the test harness can
            # grep ONE substring. The consumer-side dequeue is a pure
            # kernel-state op (the supervisor IS the kernel-of-resource),
